Type: Package
Package: splinetrials
Title: Facilitate Clinical Trials Analysis Using Natural Cubic Splines
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nik", "Krieger", , "nikolas.krieger@experis.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Daniel", "Sabanes Bove", , "daniel@rconis.com", role = "ctb"),
    person("Eli Lilly and Company", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Contains tools and helper functions that make it easier to
    run longitudinal models with continuous time. These tools include
    natural cubic splines for time data, categorization of continuous
    observed time according to scheduled visits, and trying multiple
    covariance structure types.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Imports: 
